==English==

===Noun===
'''Chironomidae'''


# scientific name for the [[chironomids]] or non-biting [[midges]], a family of true flies ([[Diptera]]) widely distributed in aquatic and semi-aquatic habitats
#:''Fossil head capsules of the Chironomidae have proven useful as indicators of past climatic change.''

